---
import { Aside } from '@astrojs/starlight/components';
---

<div class="pp-api-key-callout">
  <Aside type="note" title="Test vs live keys">
    The API key prefix determines the mode:
    <code>pp_test_…</code> hits sandbox (not billed). <code>pp_live_…</code> hits production (billed).
    Both prefixes target the same endpoint.
  </Aside>
</div>
